facts.fact: Marisa Alviar-Agnew and Henry Agnew are licensed authors of chemistry materials in LibreText.
The chemistry materials authored by Alviar-Agnew and Agnew are licensed under CK-12.
The section titled '1: The Chemical World' is part of the Introductory Chemistry materials in LibreText.
The exercises in the chemistry materials are also attributed to Marisa Alviar-Agnew and Henry Agnew.
The materials include various topics such as energy and matter.
